---
// V2 Home page — pixel-faithful Figma implementation
// Artboard: 1512px. All values fluid via var(--unit).
// Sections:
//   1. Menu (teal, top-rounded, sticky)
//   2. Hero (teal, bottom-rounded, 671px)
//   3. Projets (2 rows × 3 cols, asymmetric grid)
//   4. Méthodologie (cream bg, 3 cards)
//   5. Ils me font confiance (logo grid)
//   6. Ressources (3 cards)
//   7. Footer

